quran[14{c,v,t}:
67,13,aur tum ( log ) baat posheeda kaho ya zahir. woh dil ke bheidoon taq se waaqif hai
67,14,bhala jis ne pedakiya woh be khabar hai? woh to posheeda baton ka jan-nay wala aur ( har cheez se ) aagah hai
67,15,wohi to hai jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko naramkiya to is ki raahon mein chalo phiro aur khuda ka ( diya ho ) rizaq khao aur tum ko isi ke paas ( qabron se ) nikal kar jana hai
67,16,kiya tum is se jo aasman mein hai be khauf ho ke tum ko zameen mein dhansa day aur woh is waqt harkat karne lagey
67,17,kiya tum is se jo aasman mein hai nidar ho ke tum par kanker bhari howa chore day. so tum anqareeb jaan lau ge ke mera darana kaisa hai
67,18,aur jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne bhi jhatlaya tha so ( dekh lau ke ) mera kaisa azaab howa
67,19,kiya unhon ne apne suron par urrtay hue janwaron ko nahi dekha jo paron ko phelaaye rehtay hain aur un ko sukairh bhi letay hain. khuda ke siwa inhen koi thaam nahi sakta. be shak woh har cheez ko dekh raha hai
67,20,bhala aisa kon hai jo tumhari fouj ho kar khuda ke siwa tumhari madad kar sakay. kafir to dhokay mein hain
67,21,bhala agar woh apna rizaq band karle to kon hai jo tum ko rizaq day? lekin yeh sar kashi aur nafrat mein phansay hue hain
67,22,bhala jo shakhs chalta howa munh ke bil gir parta hai woh seedhay raste par hai ya woh jo seedhay raste par barabar chal raha ho ?
67,23,kaho woh khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko pedakiya. aur tumahray kaan aur ankhen aur dil banaye ( magar ) tum kam ahsaan mantay ho
67,24,keh do ke wohi hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein phelaya aur isi ke rubaroo tum jama kiye jao ge
67,25,aur kafir kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to yeh vayd kab ( poora ) hoga ?
67,26,keh do is ka ilm khuda hi ko hai. aur mein to khol khol kar dar sunanay dainay wala hon
